[48;5;237m                                                                                [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m## Purpose[39m                                                                      [49m
[48;5;237m                                                                                [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231mThis package is intended to define many-agents-one-assistant coordination [39m      [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231mcontracts.[39m                                                                      [49m
[48;5;237m                                                                                [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231mConsumers should expect this package to own:[39m                                    [49m
